#: content/about/news/1565568000.md:53
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid "A detailed overview of the changes between Xfce 4.12 and Xfce 4.14 releases can be found on the following page:\n"
msgstr "Një përmbledhje e hollësishme e dallimeve mes versioneve Xfce 4.12 dhe Xfce 4.16 mund të gjendet në faqen vijuese:\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1565568000.md:55 content/about/news/1425081600.md:57 content/about/news/1335571200.md:26
